In the MATTER OF the Imprisonment of: Ryan Lamar PARSONS No. 320P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 25, 2017 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, J. Douglas Henderson, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Ryan Lamar Parsons, for Parsons, Ryan Lamar.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 22nd of September 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Guilford County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 25th of September 2017."
